OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1772539378
OL,3,CTwo arrests after paramedics and
OL,4,Cpolice officers assaulted during
OL,5,C'disorder'
OL,7,FTwo people have been arrested after
OL,8,Fparamedics and police officers were
OL,9,Fassaulted during a disorder at a
OL,10,Fproperty in Swindon.
OL,12,FWiltshire Police were called to an
OL,13,Faddress in Kingswood Avenue shortly
OL,14,Fafter 12.15pm on Friday 27 February,
OL,15,Ffollowing a report that two paramedics
OL,16,Fwere being assaulted.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
