CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1772539378
OL,3,CTwo arrests after paramedics and
OL,4,Cpolice officers assaulted during
OL,5,C'disorder'
OL,7,FOfficers attended the scene where they
OL,8,Farrested a man in his 30s on suspicion
OL,9,Fof assault on an emergency worker and
OL,10,Ftwo counts of threatening to kill
OL,11,Fpolice officers.
OL,13,FA woman in her 20s was also arrested
OL,14,Fon suspicion of assaulting an
OL,15,Femergency worker. She was initially
OL,16,Ftaken to hospital for treatment and
OL,17,Fthen taken to custody.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
