FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1772539378
OL,3,CTwo arrests after paramedics and
OL,4,Cpolice officers assaulted during
OL,5,C'disorder'
OL,7,FInspector Jamie Brown of Wiltshire
OL,8,FPolice said: "We will not tolerate
OL,9,Fassaults on paramedics, police
OL,10,Fofficers, or any other emergency
OL,11,Fservice workers who are there to help
OL,12,Fand protect members of our communities.
OL,14,F"These people put themselves in
OL,15,Fdifficult situations every day to
OL,16,Fprovide urgent care and support to
OL,17,Fthose in need, and to be met with
OL,18,Fviolence whilst carrying out their
OL,19,Fduty is totally unacceptable."
OL,21,FNo serious injuries were reported.
